{"title":"抓人","authors":["札克·列努阿尔"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":8,"day":12}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"抓人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔海地〕札克·列努阿尔"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几百年啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人们受难苦连连……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恐怖的绞索"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧紧勒住我的喉管，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连喘息也困难。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"于是，我抽身逃窜……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"追赶的脚步声咚咚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像羯鼓在胸中震动。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“逃亡的黑人”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“逃亡的黑人”……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喊声愈来愈近……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"眼看就要抓住，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五花大绑……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"死难临头……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不，决不！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你们这边找"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我往那边逃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从一个水兵的胯下"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悄悄溜脱了……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶快往森林里跑！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跑呀跑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拼命逃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"像一头脱笼的困兽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我扑向自己人，我们的岗哨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——我的笑声在山谷里回响——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我投入了自由的怀抱！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔王庚年译〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}